<p>The Dawson's Creek actress looked chic in a white knit sweater that she teamed with black jeans. </p>

<p>A large black tote bag hung on her shoulder as she embraced her new love. </p>

<p>Meanwhile Emilio opted for a monochrome outfit in a brown sweater and beige slacks as he pulled her in by her waist. </p>

